1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:03,870
M: Thank you for calling Saks Fifth Avenue Department Store.
男：感谢致电萨克斯第五大道百货商店。

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:06,750
How can I be of assistance to you today?
有什么我能帮到你的吗？

3
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:12,270
W: Hello. I was in your store this past weekend and bought a few items.
女：你好。上周末我在你们店里买了几样东西。

4
00:00:12,510 --> 00:00:17,390
Yesterday, my friend told me that the annual anniversary sales had begun.
昨天我朋友告诉我周年庆促销活动已经开始了。

5
00:00:17,710 --> 00:00:23,580
It turned out she bought the same sweater as I did but for a much lower price.
结果，她和我买了件一样的毛衣，但是价格要低得多。

6
00:00:23,860 --> 00:00:27,520
M: Yes. Our anniversary sales started on Monday.
男：是的。我们的店庆促销活动周一就开始了。

7
00:00:27,970 --> 00:00:34,200
We do offer price adjustments within seven days of purchase to ensure our customers’ satisfaction.
我们确实在购物七天内做了些价格调整，确保顾客能满意。

8
00:00:34,730 --> 00:00:37,150
You said you did the purchase here this past weekend?
您说是在上周末购买的？

9
00:00:37,150 --> 00:00:41,490
W: Yes. I was shopping in your store last Sunday afternoon.
女：是的。我是上周日下午在店里买的。

10
00:00:41,490 --> 00:00:45,120
M: That would definitely fall within the price adjustment window.
男：那个时候肯定是处于调价窗口了。

11
00:00:45,830 --> 00:00:47,290
Do you have an account with us?
您有本店的账户吗？

12
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:51,260
We can credit your account directly with the difference if you wish.
如果您愿意，我们可以直接在您的账户中补偿差价。

13
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:54,900
Otherwise, we can send a gift card by mail if you prefer.
另外，若您愿意，我们也可以寄一份购物卡。

14
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:58,100
W: Crediting my account would be wonderful. Thank you.
女：账户里补偿差价更好。谢谢了。

15
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:06,730
Now that you’ve mentioned there is a sale going on, I do remember a dress I quite liked when I was in the shop on Sunday.
既然你提到了还在促销，我记得周日在店里有一条裙子我很喜欢。

16
00:01:06,730 --> 00:01:08,010
Is it on offer as well?
这条裙子也打折吗？

17
00:01:08,010 --> 00:01:12,900
M: Yes, ma’am. All the new arrivals are 15-20% off.
男：是的，女士。所有新款都打八五折到八折。

18
00:01:13,420 --> 00:01:18,320
In addition to the sale, we are running a promotion for complementary tailoring if needed.
除了打折，我们还有个免费裁剪的促销活动，如果您需要的话。

19
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:20,120
W: That’s good news.
女：这可太好了。
